---
title: Raw Bites
---

<div class='row header'>
  <div class='container-fluid'>
    <div class='col-md-12 col-sm-12 pb-3'>
      <%= image_tag('new_logo.png', :class =>'logo img-fluid pt-1') %>
      <div class='text text-xs-center mt-1'>
        <h6 class='subtitle'><span class='text-aqua'>COMING SOON</span> THE FIRST</h6>
        <h4 class='headline'>healthy snack<br>subscription box</h4>
        <h6 class='subtitle'>IN THE PHILIPPINES</h6>
      </div>
      <%= image_tag('box_items.png', :class =>'hero img-fluid pt-1') %>
      <div class='row text-center mt-1'>
        <%= partial 'partials/mailing_list' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class='row mt-1 why-subscribe pb-5'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='col-md-10 col-sm-12 offset-md-1'>
      <%= image_tag('why_subscribe.png', :class =>'img-fluid mb-1 hidden-xs-down') %>
      <%= image_tag('why_subscribe-mobile.png', :class =>'img-fluid mb-1 hidden-sm-up') %>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-12 col-sm-12 text-center mt-1 mb-2'>
      <p>Discover up to 15 of the greatest health snacks.</p>
      <p>Think the newest superfoods, wholefood bars, nut butters, veggie and fruit chips, protein balls, raw chocolates, freeze dried fruits, super blends or gluten-free cereals – that’s just an idea of what you might get.</p>
  </div>
  <div class='features mb-3'>
    <div class='col-md-4 offset-md-1 col-sm-12 text-center'>
      <%= image_tag('open_box.png', :class =>'img-fluid') %>
      <h6 class='title'>Box Type</h6>
      <p>Pick from a trial, regular, or premium box; the higher you go, the
  more snacks you get</p>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-4 offset-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center'>
        <%= image_tag('green_calendar.png', :class =>'img-fluid') %>
      <h6 class='title'>Subscription Period</h6>
      <p>Choose from a monthly, 3- 6- 12-month payment plan. Payment automatically renews every after period.</p>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-4 offset-md-1 col-sm-12 text-center'>
        <%= image_tag('money.png', :class =>'img-fluid ') %>
      <h6 class='title'>Cost</h6>
      <p>Start at P995 per box. Subscribe to a longer period on the Regular or Premium plan to get more savings</p>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-4 offset-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-3'>
        <%= image_tag('grey_calendar.png', :class =>'img-fluid') %>
      <h6 class='title'>Cancellation</h6>
      <p>All plans can be paused at any time.<br>
  If you're not satisfied, you can cancel your plan at least 10 days prior to auto-renewal</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
